<title>USA: Bank of Hemet to buy back shares.</title>
<headline>Bank of Hemet to buy back shares.</headline>
<dateline>HEMET, Calif 1997-01-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Bank of Hemet said on Thursday it planned to buy back up to 10 percent of its outstanding shares in common stock as a way to reduce excess capital.</p>
<p>The bank said it had yet to decide the price at which it will buy the shares.</p>
<p>The bank said it will make the repurchase in the form of a tender offer to all shareholders, beginning within the next two months.</p>
